    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "a reading that low right before touchdown... that almost sounds like they were landing on something much more solid or structural than just regolith. like they hit a roof or a platform. if that 'glitch' was actually them landing on a structure, what kind of data would they be trying to hide? was there anything else in those logs about the visual telemetry or the radio silence during that specific window?",
